FBIS3-4298 "drchi060_d_94017" FBIS-CHI-94-060 Document Type:Daily Report 29 Mar 1994 Northeast Asia ROK Firm Offers Loans for Thermal Power Plants OW2903105894 Beijing XINHUA in English 1043 GMT 29 Mar 94 OW2903105894 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, March 29 (XINHUA) -- The East Asia Construction Industry Corporation Ltd. from the Republic of Korea (ROK) will offer loans to build two thermal power plants in China. The total installed capacity of the two power plants will reach more than 300,000 kw. The corporation signed a cooperation agreement with China and the U.S. here recently. The corporation is a leading power plant construction engineering corporation in the Republic of Korea.
